				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I want a Sony rep to post and state that the 52, 58, and 63 have been tested vs mobs of the appropriate level, and that there's a good excuse for their having the least hitpoints of any of our pets.
<br />

<br />
I maintain that they are substandard (as will any mage on the board), and need some dang work.  Increase Kindle to do 50 mana/tick, or better yet, remove the wizard crap from them entirely and make them summon in with a pair of NODROP (can't give to other pets), No-race (i.e. pet only) weapons that are 1 damage, 20 delay, and have ~35, ~40, and ~50 fire damage, respectively.  Or a 2H weapon with 2x that damage, etc.  If those values aren't good enough, I'm sure the DPS math is available to the developers to make them worthy of having the fewest hits, and worst mitigation, of any mage pet.
<br />

<br />
Please fix them!  It sucks that no mage has been able to summon anything worthwhile from the Elemental Plane of Fire for like 4 years now.<br />_________________<br />Arhallia Ironborne
<br />
<span style="color: red">65th Arch Convoker</span>
<br />
Toenan Twosoks
<br />
