			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Dispel no longer dispells detrimentals on an opponent.  Thus it no longer wipes out malosi, tash, etc.  Just takes care of damage shields, buffs, other irritating stuff a mob has put on itself.
<br />

<br />
Thus the fire pet casting it on the opponent is never a bad thing these days.<br />_________________<br />Arhallia Ironborne
